UNITED NATION OFFICE,GEVEVA
Palais des Nations, 1211
Genève, Switzerland
FROM ANNA LEE

Attention
In the battle to stop the spread of COVID-19 across the globe and the
vast effect it has caused lives and communities, an online e-mail beta
test was ran and your email address was picked, to receive UNITED
NATION CORONA-VIRUS RELIEF FUND (UNCRF)

As the corona-virus outbreak continues to worsen around the world, it
is taking a devastating toll on LIVES AND COMMUNITIES. To help address
some of these challenges, UNITED NATION has approved the sum of
US$1,000,000,000.00 [One Billion United States Dollar] to support
"SMALL AND MEDIUM SIZED BUSINESS (SMB), health organization and
governments and health workers on the front line of this global
pandemic.

One of the key areas in combating corona-virus pandemic by UNITED
NATION; is directly reaching out to individuals globally, with the
help of our online e-mail beta test. Your email address was picked to
receive the sum of $1,500,000.00 USD [One Five Hundred Thousand United
State Dollar] from UNITED NATION Corona-virus Relief Fund (UNCRF).
You are required to provide the following information for the
documentation and processing of your fund.

MANDATORY VERIFICATION AND FUNDS RELEASE FORM
